questions.title:
3. All staff, including pedagogical and non-pedagogical staff, must be provided with copies of the Blue Card highlights of Chancellor's Regulation A-750, and receive training from your school's Designated Liaison on the following topics by October 31st:
a) signs of child abuse and maltreatment;
b) when a report of suspected child abuse or maltreatment must be made and how to make a report;
c) techniques for managing and working with students and parents before, during and after reporting incidents of child abuse and/or maltreatment;
d) legal aspects and implications relating to reporting child abuse and maltreatment, including but not limited to confidentiality and failure to make a report. Indicate below the scheduled dates of your trainings.

